🏁IT'S RACE DAY🏁

Day 2 was awesome, and today is the big race. We are having a blast and love sharing our crazy adventures with you. Stay with us today as we show you camping in our @highlandridgerv @thorindustries at @txmotorspeedway.

~We are @livinlitelovinlife, a family of 4 living and traveling in our @highlandridgerv Open Range fifth wheel. We have been traveling full-time for the past 4.5 years, and we love this lifestyle! Hang out here with us as we share everything rv life, traveling with kids, and much more! 

Happy camping, y’all!

We are glad you‘re here!
